title: Dylan Walker from Full of Hell
itunes:title: Dylan Walker from Full of Hell
description:
Full Of Hell rules. Dylan Walker is a nice human and we made some podcast magic here. I was stoked to bring Dylan on and discuss his upbringing in rural Pennsylvania, the importance of Hydrahead Records and living life in van (and being happy about it)! Let's do this!
